Unit test cases:

For ProductController:

1. Unit test for getting all products when there are no products
2. Unit test for getting all products when there are few products
3. Unit test for getting all products with valid brand id and invalid brand id
4. Unit test for getting all products with valid color and invalid color
5. Unit test for getting all products with valid and invalid size
6. Unit test for getting all products with valid color and invalid price

For SellerProductController:

1. Unit test for getting number of units for a valid and invalid seller id
2. Unit test for getting number of units for a valid and invalid sku values